author: Daniel Newhauser, Keegan Hamilton, Michael Learmonth
title: Chinese Drug Dealers Have A New Product: Knock-Off N95 Masks for Coronavirus
description: “They're supplying them through the same exact supply chain, through the same exact marketing mechanisms, that they have with illicit drugs for a long time.”
